{"type": "article", "id": 4131, "title": "(multee)project 登山扣", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-05T08:25:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233057OMTRm7K3HqzYIaVF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自美国加州的配饰品牌 (multee)project 日前推出了两款最新单品登山扣，在外形设计上，品牌选择以旗下的经典产品 Type-2L Carabiner 位基础进行再设计，采用了金色与银铜色两种金属物料分别制作而成，搭配了 (multee)project 标志性的皮革用以装饰，并将其 logo 印于皮革之上。定价 108 美元，<a href=\"http://multeeproject.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523305571pNrE2ASaLMCnzk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052330565nmDz7I2ojaFeXAy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233056DL8KhzvVPAe7HrxZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}